<Author>A TripAdvisor Member
<Content>In the Middle of The Night Life After many visits to Mexico City, I seem to always return to the Krystal Rosa to stay. It may not be the most luxurious, but the location makes it my choice. The Krystal Rosa is conveniently located in the Zona Rosa area of Mexico City. This is a beautifull area with restaurants, shops and a blocked street for pedestrians only. It is the gathering spot for many of the local night set groups. There is food, music and action. The Krystal is also just two blocks from the Insurgentes Metro stop.Rooms are simple and adequatley furnished. The staff is superb! The food in the hotel is little better than most of the fancy restaurants in Mexico City, just barely adequate. But then why eat fancy in Mexico when great local food abounds. The Krystal Rosa is near to the action and is classy. 
